reviews.review_text: 5 at garden Live on the island 35min train to nyc. saw 5 nights and got to sleep in my own bed.Not the greatest shows ever (saw 1st in 1980) but still always magical to me!Not rating the sound quality or 1 particular show ,just the 5 night event
